Dialogue: 0,00:05:35.000,00:05:41.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,my E is going to amplify to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:41.000,00:05:45.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.000,00:05:52.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,And the norm of a matrix in MATLAB,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.000,00:05:54.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,you can just type norm.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:54.000,00:05:55.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,All right.
