Dialogue: 0,00:06:05.000,00:06:09.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Is it for any vector E?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:09.000,00:06:12.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So the definition of the norm is for any vector E.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.000,00:06:14.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,And the maximization is for any vector E.
